sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor KH as Khach hang
    participant GW as API Gateway
    participant Order as Order Service
    participant OrderDB as Order DB

    KH->>GW: PUT /api/orders/my-orders/:orderId/cancel
    Note over KH,GW: reason tuy chon
    GW->>Order: Forward request - yeu cau auth CUSTOMER

    Order->>OrderDB: order.findById(orderId)
    OrderDB-->>Order: order record

    alt Don hang khong ton tai
        Order-->>GW: 404 Not Found
        GW-->>KH: Don hang khong ton tai
    else Don hang khong thuoc ve khach hang nay
        Order-->>GW: 403 Forbidden
        GW-->>KH: Khong co quyen huy don hang nay
    else Trang thai khong cho phep huy
        Note over Order: Chi huy duoc khi status<br/>la PENDING hoac PENDING_PAYMENT
        Order-->>GW: 400 Bad Request
        GW-->>KH: Khong the huy don hang o trang thai nay
    else Co the huy
        Order->>OrderDB: order.update - status=CANCELLED
        Order->>OrderDB: statusLog.create
        Note over Order,OrderDB: changed_by=customerId<br/>old_status, reason, timestamp
        OrderDB-->>Order: order da cap nhat

        Order-->>GW: 200 OK
        Note over Order,GW: orderId, orderCode<br/>status=CANCELLED
        GW-->>KH: Don hang da huy thanh cong
    end

